## Key Conventions

- Read `.planning/CURRENT.md` before starting work — it contains the active task and last checkpoint.
- Check `.planning/DECISIONS.md` before proposing architecture changes.
- **Never invent** library method names — check `docs/external-apis/` or the official docs first.
- One logical change per commit: `<type>: <short description>`
- Do not commit `TODO`/`FIXME` without a `.planning/DECISIONS.md` entry.

## Security

- Never write API keys, tokens, or secrets into code or commit messages.
- SQL only via parameterized queries.
- Flag auth/crypto/payments/PII code for review before committing.

